@startuml
title UC-FR-03 User Account Management
left to right direction

actor "Administrator" as Admin

rectangle "Academic Management System" {
  (Create User Account) as Create
  (View User Accounts) as View
  (Edit User Account) as Edit
  (Activate/Deactivate User) as Active
  (Assign/Remove Roles) as Roles

  (Validate User Data) as Validate
  (Reject User Operation) as Reject
}

Admin -- Create
Admin -- View
Admin -- Edit
Admin -- Active
Admin -- Roles

Create ..> Validate : <<include>>
Edit ..> Validate : <<include>>
Roles ..> Validate : <<include>>
Reject ..> Create : <<extend>>
Reject ..> Edit : <<extend>>

note right of Reject
Triggered when:
- email already exists
- invalid role
- user not found
end note

@enduml
